updates.update_content:
We are currently making progress with our manufacturer on component specifications, but in the meantime we have some updates for you; 
Big Upgrades to the Tabletop Simulator version! 
While playtesting Mantis Falls over the last several years, we have used Tabletop Simulator on Steam to play with friends and family from afar. We wanted that option to be available to others who enjoy digital tabletop gaming, especially right now.
